# Luau conventions

- Keep changes consistent with the repo’s existing architecture and naming.
- Don’t guess Roblox APIs: confirm with `node cursor/scripts/api-dump.js ...` when exact signatures or members matter.
- Separate confirmed facts (dump/docs) from inference when answering questions.

